{"tid":1662581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《衰仔樂園》又玩嘢！ 抄占士「舔共」名句諷踐踏言論自由","createTime":"2019-10-19T00:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T08:57:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ca1f2fdb3fa6dfa3b3fc81c015843a3d8e93fd27","tid":1662581,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:43:08.000Z","msg":"美國長壽卡通《衰仔樂園》（《South Park》；內地稱《南方樂園》），以黑色幽默手法諷刺時政聞名。最近一期節目再延續前2周的火力，繼續炮轟中國「沒自由」，這一集更暗諷美國NBA洛杉磯湖人球星勒邦占士（LeBron James）「舔共」。<br />\n<br />\n在美國時間周三播出的這一集《衰仔樂園》，主題為「讓他們吃稠稠物 （Let Them Eat Goo）」。故事講述衰仔樂園小學收到一些學生投訴，指營養午餐應該更健康，因此校方決定更改午餐配方，標榜更有營養。但新推出的午餐食譜，引發愛吃垃圾食物的Cartman不滿，更因此和同學鬧翻。同學對Cartman說，他們有言論自由，有權抗議不健康的午餐，而Cartman反擊：「對，我們的確擁有言論自由，但是，當你沒有考慮別人而只考慮自己的時候，有時會產生負面的後果。」<br />\n<br />\nCartman這段台詞，完全和日前勒邦占士的聲明如出一轍。勒邦占士周一針對火箭總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）支持香港反送中的Twitter留言表達看法，勒邦占士直言：「對，我們有言論自由，但也有可能因而引發很多負面的影響。我不想與莫利因為一字一句而爭吵，但我認為他表態前，沒有對相關情況（反送中抗爭）掌握足夠的資訊。很多人可能因此受到傷害，無論是在經濟上或是身心上。我們對發tweet、說甚麼和做甚麼都必須小心。」<br />\n<br />\n《衰仔樂園》最新一季（第23季）第2集《Band in China》，故意影射小熊維尼、器官移植等話題諷刺中國，結果遭中國封殺，《衰仔樂園》隨即發文以嘲諷的語調「道歉」：「跟NBA一樣，我們歡迎中國審查我們的家和我們的內心，我們也熱愛金錢勝過熱愛自由和民主。」在上周的節目中，《衰仔樂園》直接用髒話大肆批評中國踐踏自由人權。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191018/large/1571397456_a9d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191018%2Flarge%2F1571397456_a9d1.jpg&h=08b798a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191018/60169739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F60169739&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9nwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=ba07e30d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F60169739&h=4ed74d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191018/60169739</a>"},{"pid":"1c77a22cfd9619add30b3947cf9cf40c3b1ce66c","tid":1662581,"uid":33711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:45:09.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24df0e141cc4fcf7118dcd8676a192d51dff463","tid":1662581,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:48:52.000Z","msg":"邊到有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9467729e8f32154c44efec1afbe7684ebc423e","tid":1662581,"uid":23390,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24df0e141cc4fcf7118dcd8676a192d51dff463","tid":1662581,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:48:52.000Z","msg":"邊到有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:49:27.000Z","msg":"Netflix 都有"},{"pid":"2389970e94778f710ca31dde30c9db5119b4d383","tid":1662581,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:50:16.000Z","msg":"其實如果冇中文解釋淨係睇片 有啲睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b7043dd7d3422b39794a6f9c399b820912090d","tid":1662581,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d810b0853617416d7fc08a54eef1fb7aa1476d5c","tid":1662581,"uid":306949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71706b129cd9172924b45dc166eb30139b9c754","tid":1662581,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2389970e94778f710ca31dde30c9db5119b4d383","tid":1662581,"uid":23390,"like":0,"disl